<item>
            <title>[HBASE-10744] AM#CloseRegion no need to retry on FailedServerException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10744</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a regionserver restarts, AM#CloseRegion could get FailedServerException, or ServerNotRunningYetException. The call should not be retried since we know the original regionserver should be down.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
